{"tid":1739003,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[理大手足] 已經有第一批被控暴動上庭 千萬唔好投降","createTime":"2019-11-19T12:20:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T13:26:21.000Z","uid":103842,"like":135,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"6d05f5a08fa212aa3332a30cd1c107a55bceed46","tid":1739003,"uid":103842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:20:46.000Z","msg":"西九龍裁判法院第三庭 <br />\n控告所有被告 #1118理大暴動<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府惡行</span></span><br />\n有手足被控方拒絕保釋<br />\n羈留15小時內多番要求用膳 但被拒絕<br />\n未有法律意見下被要求穿上gear影相 加強控告你入罪<br />\n被制服後<br />\n被警棍擊打手臂<br />\n遭地面拖行長時間<br />\n拖行期間被警棍毆打<br />\n壓在地上導致門牙崩一半<br />\n速龍用磚攻擊<br />\n蒙面無編號速龍：帶你地去新屋嶺雞姦<br />\n被恐嚇「番到去打到你爆缸」<br />\n被制服後，近距離以橡膠子彈射擊<br />\n被噴胡椒噴霧<br />\n被辱罵(分別以廣東話及普通話)<br />\n要求睇醫生，但到現時未獲准求醫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以上就係投降既後果 政府同狗係萬萬不能相信<br />\n狗隊同林鄭承受唔起光洲事件同64天安門事件係香港再發生 所以先會勸降<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">留係理大係最好既選擇 一個都不能少 </span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6e9d7c8daf08e370c064a0ce37948f790c81411","tid":1739003,"uid":48868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:21:38.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0befee4a240b7a0df5b003f65416fd859f6aba","tid":1739003,"uid":20870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:22:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4af728f14b08ebf71cfc778d8b8870ab3bf3a2","tid":1739003,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:23:35.000Z","msg":"仆街狗"},{"pid":"410547a57daf0